            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Ultra-Light Performance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Pro-grade sound with minimal CPU and RAM. More music in your DAW, less strain on your system.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-xl bg-[#1a1a1a] flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-[#E94560]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Simple Interface</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">A clean workspace that keeps you focused on creating, not configuring. No sea of knobs and faders.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DAW Compatibility Section -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 border-t border-[#1a1a1a]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">Works with your favorite DAW</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
